            "answer_text": "The very famous song Jab pyar kiya to darna kya from Mughal-E-Aazam starts with the raaga Darbari (where only Taan is heard) and moves on to the song which is based on raaga Durga. The music was composed by Naushad Ji. The song was formed from a folk song of Uttar Pradesh \u2018Prem kiya kya chori kari hai'. The folk song was converted into Ghazal form with the modified lyrics and then moulded it to the beautiful music which we hear today. ",
